{"type":"message","id":"2755ea1c","parentId":"ac9e450b","timestamp":"2026-05-20T18:21:02.820Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Thu 2026-05-21 02:20 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 修复 WASM SDK 登录时机问题：\n\n**问题**：`clickLogin2()` 在 credentials API 成功后被调用，但此时 WASM SDK 的 `cbInitPluginComplete` 可能还没完成，导致 `I_Login` 无法执行。\n\n**修复要求**：\n\n在 `cbInitPluginComplete` 回调中添加检查并触发登录：\n\n找到 WASM SDK 初始化代码（大约在文件末尾）：\n```javascript\ncbInitPluginComplete: function() {\n    console.log('[WASM] cbInitPluginComplete - inserting plugin');\n    WebVideoCtrl.I_InsertOBJECTPlugin(\"divPlugin\");\n    // WASM SDK ready - login/play happens when user clicks connect\n}\n```\n\n修改为：\n```javascript\ncbInitPluginComplete: function() {\n    console.log('[WASM] cbInitPluginComplete - inserting plugin');\n    WebVideoCtrl.I_InsertOBJECTPlugin(\"divPlugin\");\n    // WASM SDK ready - trigger login if device already connected\n    if (window.connectedDevice && window.connectedDevice.ip && window.clickLogin2) {\n        console.log('[WASM] Device already connected, triggering login');\n        window.clickLogin2();\n    }\n}\n```\n\n文件路径：D:\\astro_py\\astro_hub\\src\\web\\base.html\n\n修复后不要过度开发，不要添加其他功能。"}],"timestamp":1779301262807}}
