{"type":"message","id":"d97a4755","parentId":"ae3aa024","timestamp":"2026-05-20T18:22:32.304Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Done. Let me summarize the task completion.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## ✅ 修复完成\n\n**文件**: `D:\\astro_py\\astro_hub\\src\\web\\base.html`\n\n**变更**: `cbInitPluginComplete` 回调中添加了登录触发逻辑：\n\n```javascript\ncbInitPluginComplete: function() {\n    console.log('[WASM] cbInitPluginComplete - inserting plugin');\n    WebVideoCtrl.I_InsertOBJECTPlugin(\"divPlugin\");\n    // WASM SDK ready - trigger login if device already connected\n    if (window.connectedDevice && window.connectedDevice.ip && window.clickLogin2) {\n        console.log('[WASM] Device already connected, triggering login');\n        window.clickLogin2();\n    }\n},\n```\n\n**原理**: 当 credentials API 先设置了 `window.connectedDevice`，但 WASM SDK 初始化还未完成时，`clickLogin2()` 会失败。现在在 `cbInitPluginComplete`（WASM SDK 真正就绪时）中检查是否已有连接设备，如果有则自动触发登录。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"YerPlan","model":"qwen3.6-plus","usage":{"input":18446,"output":224,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18670,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779301345075,"responseId":"chatcmpl-8eda4cf2-7f36-90be-8526-9950b8f2597c"}}
